1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,719
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:32,274
=Episode 22=
(Fate turns in endless cycles)

3
00:00:32,275 --> 00:00:34,282
(and won't rest till it's resolved.)

4
00:00:40,020 --> 00:00:41,260
I want this.

5
00:00:44,180 --> 00:00:44,859
No.

6
00:00:44,860 --> 00:00:45,779
Baobao!

7
00:00:45,780 --> 00:00:46,860
Baobao!

8
00:00:47,020 --> 00:00:47,779
Stop right there!

9
00:00:47,780 --> 00:00:49,180
Mother!

10
00:00:50,180 --> 00:00:51,019
Baobao!

11
00:00:51,020 --> 00:00:52,579
- I need some water.
- Mother, Mother!

12
00:00:52,580 --> 00:00:53,980
Fine, I won't fight you for it.

13
00:00:54,700 --> 00:00:56,020
I won't take it.

14
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:01,619
Open the door!

15
00:01:01,620 --> 00:01:03,459
Physician! Physician!

16
00:01:03,460 --> 00:01:05,299
Help, please save me!

17
00:01:05,300 --> 00:01:06,979
Help! Help!

18
00:01:06,980 --> 00:01:08,139
Please save us!

19
00:01:08,140 --> 00:01:09,419
Save the child!

20
00:01:09,420 --> 00:01:10,379
Sir, please save us!

21
00:01:10,380 --> 00:01:13,179
Sir! Sir! Please!

22
00:01:13,180 --> 00:01:15,099
Please save us!

23
00:01:15,100 --> 00:01:16,860
Open the door, Physician!

24
00:01:19,100 --> 00:01:20,780
Please save us!

25
00:01:21,820 --> 00:01:24,020
I'm begging you!

26
00:01:27,820 --> 00:01:30,099
I don't want to die!

27
00:01:30,100 --> 00:01:31,419
Save me!

28
00:01:31,420 --> 00:01:33,339
Open the door!

29
00:01:33,340 --> 00:01:34,379
(Buns)
Zhao!

30
00:01:34,380 --> 00:01:35,460
I'm here.

31
00:01:35,740 --> 00:01:37,780
Mother, I'll help too.

32
00:01:37,980 --> 00:01:40,340
Your Highness, I await your orders.

33
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:42,620
(Fate has given the same problem again.)

34
00:01:42,980 --> 00:01:44,900
(This time, I will solve it.)

35
00:01:50,060 --> 00:01:51,860
Your Highness! General!

36
00:01:51,980 --> 00:01:53,259
Something terrible has happened!

37
00:01:53,260 --> 00:01:55,320
All the Flower Slaves
have been released by Helian Shu!

38
00:01:55,620 --> 00:01:57,380
My father and the people in the prison

39
00:01:58,780 --> 00:02:00,380
have all been killed!

40
00:02:00,980 --> 00:02:02,259
Helian Shu!

41
00:02:02,260 --> 00:02:03,740
Xiao, stay calm.

42
00:02:09,180 --> 00:02:12,140
Immediately bring the Pei Army
stationed outside into the city.

43
00:02:12,420 --> 00:02:14,259
Move all infected civilians

44
00:02:14,260 --> 00:02:16,020
to Baihua Hall outside the city.

45
00:02:16,340 --> 00:02:17,619
Then await my orders.

46
00:02:17,620 --> 00:02:19,580
Xiao, go to the palace.

47
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:21,899
Report this situation to the Emperor.

48
00:02:21,900 --> 00:02:23,140
Yes, Your Highness.

49
00:02:23,540 --> 00:02:25,580
Your Highness, there's one more thing.

50
00:02:25,620 --> 00:02:28,139
Helian Shu and his shadow guards

51
00:02:28,140 --> 00:02:29,740
have a red flower growing on them.

52
00:02:30,260 --> 00:02:31,500
It's very strange.

53
00:02:32,260 --> 00:02:34,220
Could this Verdant Decay

54
00:02:35,180 --> 00:02:36,860
be connected to Helian Shu?

55
00:02:37,180 --> 00:02:39,100
Then, when did he get infected?

56
00:02:42,700 --> 00:02:43,940
You wretch!

57
00:02:46,420 --> 00:02:48,340
(It's been a hundred years.)

58
00:02:48,500 --> 00:02:50,420
(I've finally awakened.)

59
00:02:51,300 --> 00:02:53,620
(I really want a bite of meat.)

60
00:02:56,940 --> 00:02:57,900
You...

61
00:02:58,140 --> 00:02:59,219
Your eyes...

62
00:02:59,220 --> 00:03:01,499
(I'll start with you.)

63
00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:02,580
Your Majesty, run!

64
00:03:08,740 --> 00:03:10,780
Helian Shu has gone mad!

65
00:03:10,860 --> 00:03:12,060
I've obtained Stellar Dew.

66
00:03:12,300 --> 00:03:13,900
The root-seeking worm
will be ready tonight.

67
00:03:14,540 --> 00:03:15,739
Once it's done,

68
00:03:15,740 --> 00:03:17,220
I'll go to Baihua Hall to find you.

69
00:03:18,980 --> 00:03:20,459
Then, I'll protect Mother

70
00:03:20,460 --> 00:03:21,780
from the Flower Slaves.

71
00:03:22,580 --> 00:03:23,900
We'll meet at Baihua Hall.

72
00:03:27,860 --> 00:03:30,740
Sir, please!

73
00:03:31,700 --> 00:03:32,740
Quiet!

74
00:03:33,460 --> 00:03:35,020
Please save us!

75
00:03:35,140 --> 00:03:36,580
Everyone, listen to me.

76
00:03:40,300 --> 00:03:41,299
Your Highness,

77
00:03:41,300 --> 00:03:42,859
all infected civilians in the city

78
00:03:42,860 --> 00:03:44,340
have been moved to the main hall.

79
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:45,860
The physicians are in the side hall.

80
00:03:47,060 --> 00:03:48,819
Do not station troops in the main hall.

81
00:03:48,820 --> 00:03:50,299
Don't frighten the patients.

82
00:03:50,300 --> 00:03:52,899
Have the soldiers patrol nearby.

83
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:53,900
Yes.

84
00:03:54,020 --> 00:03:55,179
We've never seen this disease before.

85
00:03:55,180 --> 00:03:56,059
That's right.

86
00:03:56,060 --> 00:03:57,739
What are we supposed to do?

87
00:03:57,740 --> 00:03:59,339
It's a natural disaster!

88
00:03:59,340 --> 00:04:00,740
Such a strange illness.

89
00:04:01,020 --> 00:04:03,780
Everyone, I'll keep this brief.

90
00:04:04,460 --> 00:04:06,340
This disease is called Verdant Decay.

91
00:04:06,460 --> 00:04:08,060
The vile plant thrives
when it touches water

92
00:04:08,420 --> 00:04:10,019
and feeds on human flesh and blood.

93
00:04:10,020 --> 00:04:11,640
When the flower falls, the person dies.

94
00:04:11,980 --> 00:04:13,740
If the pollen touches a human body,

95
00:04:13,820 --> 00:04:15,740
it takes root and sprouts immediately,

96
00:04:15,980 --> 00:04:17,340
repeating the cycle.

97
00:04:17,740 --> 00:04:19,139
Such a strange disease...

98
00:04:19,140 --> 00:04:20,699
I've practiced medicine for decades

99
00:04:20,700 --> 00:04:22,220
and never heard of it.

100
00:04:22,540 --> 00:04:24,019
I've heard of it before.

101
00:04:24,020 --> 00:04:25,859
A hundred years ago, it appeared once.

102
00:04:25,860 --> 00:04:27,739
But overnight,

103
00:04:27,740 --> 00:04:29,620
all the patients disappeared.

104
00:04:29,860 --> 00:04:31,179
May I ask, miss?

105
00:04:31,180 --> 00:04:33,339
What happens if we forcibly

106
00:04:33,340 --> 00:04:34,900
remove the plant?

107
00:04:35,140 --> 00:04:37,340
The plant's roots
run through the blood vessels.

108
00:04:37,860 --> 00:04:39,579
If forcibly removed,

109
00:04:39,580 --> 00:04:42,139
the roots will invade
the organs instantly,

110
00:04:42,140 --> 00:04:43,579
and the patient will die on the spot.

111
00:04:43,580 --> 00:04:45,299
What should we do?

112
00:04:45,300 --> 00:04:46,299
Is this truly a disaster?

113
00:04:46,300 --> 00:04:47,859
- What do we do?
- What do we do?

114
00:04:47,860 --> 00:04:48,579
Yeah!

115
00:04:48,580 --> 00:04:49,580
Quiet!

116
00:04:53,020 --> 00:04:55,460
Everyone, I have a solution.

117
00:04:55,500 --> 00:04:56,459
First,

118
00:04:56,460 --> 00:04:58,620
keep the plant away from water.

119
00:04:59,260 --> 00:05:00,380
Second,

120
00:05:01,020 --> 00:05:03,859
those not infected
must wear masks and gloves.

121
00:05:03,860 --> 00:05:05,379
Do not expose bare skin.

122
00:05:05,380 --> 00:05:07,059
Cover the plant with gauze

123
00:05:07,060 --> 00:05:08,380
to prevent spread.

124
00:05:08,620 --> 00:05:11,620
Third, prepare tonics
that restore energy

125
00:05:11,700 --> 00:05:13,340
to calm everyone.

126
00:05:13,500 --> 00:05:14,780
Fourth...

127
00:05:20,380 --> 00:05:22,700
Follow these three steps
to control the disease first.

128
00:05:22,820 --> 00:05:24,820
Then, I'll explain step four.

129
00:05:41,180 --> 00:05:42,140
Everyone,

130
00:05:42,580 --> 00:05:45,260
General Pei has summoned
all the best physicians in the capital.

131
00:05:45,380 --> 00:05:46,940
We will cure every single one of you.

132
00:05:47,300 --> 00:05:48,580
Please rest assured.

133
00:05:49,260 --> 00:05:50,580
During this time,

134
00:05:50,700 --> 00:05:52,299
all food, clothing,

135
00:05:52,300 --> 00:05:53,579
medical costs,

136
00:05:53,580 --> 00:05:55,379
and even lost wages

137
00:05:55,380 --> 00:05:57,020
will be covered by the General's Manor.

138
00:05:57,260 --> 00:05:58,819
Please stay here with peace of mind.

139
00:05:58,820 --> 00:05:59,619
That's great!

140
00:05:59,620 --> 00:06:03,259
We trust the physicians!

141
00:06:03,260 --> 00:06:04,380
Next,

142
00:06:05,060 --> 00:06:06,499
we'll rely on all of you, gentlemen.

143
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:08,260
- Understood!
- Understood!

144
00:06:12,060 --> 00:06:14,380
Your Highness, please come with me.

145
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:16,500
Where to?

146
00:06:17,020 --> 00:06:18,940
The people are the priority right now.

147
00:06:29,620 --> 00:06:31,500
Your Majesty, Her Highness has arrived.

148
00:06:36,380 --> 00:06:37,500
I take my leave.

149
00:06:41,740 --> 00:06:42,900
Greetings,

150
00:06:43,620 --> 00:06:45,580
Your Majesty.

151
00:06:47,060 --> 00:06:48,460
It's only been a few days,

152
00:06:49,580 --> 00:06:53,020
yet you seem to have endured a lot.

153
00:06:53,060 --> 00:06:55,500
All thanks to you, Your Majesty.

154
00:06:56,940 --> 00:06:58,140
Come forward.

155
00:07:09,860 --> 00:07:10,940
What's wrong with you?

156
00:07:30,500 --> 00:07:32,140
The imperial physician has seen me.

157
00:07:33,700 --> 00:07:35,340
The poison has reached my heart.

158
00:07:35,700 --> 00:07:37,020
There's no cure.

159
00:07:39,820 --> 00:07:41,140
Who poisoned you?

160
00:07:43,620 --> 00:07:46,140
It's all because of Helian Shu.

161
00:07:47,180 --> 00:07:50,780
Your mother had long
suffered from illness.

162
00:07:51,180 --> 00:07:53,020
That was also his doing.

163
00:07:53,740 --> 00:07:55,820
Helian Shu!

164
00:07:56,820 --> 00:07:57,940
Xihe,

165
00:07:59,300 --> 00:08:01,580
I don't have much time left.

166
00:08:02,060 --> 00:08:05,380
Let me finish.

167
00:08:09,620 --> 00:08:11,020
Lately,

168
00:08:11,820 --> 00:08:13,820
I often dream of your mother.

169
00:08:14,940 --> 00:08:16,380
In my dreams,

170
00:08:17,020 --> 00:08:19,260
she always asks me
to see you one last time,

171
00:08:20,740 --> 00:08:23,620
to say what must be said,

172
00:08:24,620 --> 00:08:26,620
so I won't meet her

173
00:08:27,940 --> 00:08:29,500
with regrets.

174
00:08:32,460 --> 00:08:34,180
When you were born,

175
00:08:34,260 --> 00:08:35,900
the nation had just stabilized,

176
00:08:36,260 --> 00:08:37,900
and the court was in turmoil.

177
00:08:38,860 --> 00:08:40,700
The farther I kept you,

178
00:08:41,580 --> 00:08:43,380
the safer you were.

179
00:08:44,820 --> 00:08:46,379
I'm not a bird in a cage!

180
00:08:46,380 --> 00:08:48,180
I can wield blades,

181
00:08:48,260 --> 00:08:50,019
study strategy,

182
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:51,499
and master the art of balance!

183
00:08:51,500 --> 00:08:53,379
I've never been inferior to anyone.

184
00:08:53,380 --> 00:08:54,820
I know.

185
00:08:55,620 --> 00:08:57,460
I know all of it.

186
00:08:57,500 --> 00:08:59,060
Xihe,

187
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:01,820
you've never been inferior to anyone.

188
00:09:22,580 --> 00:09:24,900
It's my first time being a father.

189
00:09:26,300 --> 00:09:28,380
I didn't do as well as your mother.

190
00:09:30,700 --> 00:09:34,140
I don't expect your forgiveness.

191
00:09:35,820 --> 00:09:37,140
I only hope

192
00:09:37,900 --> 00:09:41,500
to ease the hatred in your heart.

193
00:09:42,540 --> 00:09:44,100
The edict of succession

194
00:09:44,700 --> 00:09:46,500
is already written.

195
00:09:48,940 --> 00:09:51,260
Once I remove

196
00:09:51,580 --> 00:09:53,620
all the corrupt officials...

197
00:09:53,700 --> 00:09:54,860
I hold

198
00:09:57,300 --> 00:09:58,780
no grudge.

199
00:10:01,780 --> 00:10:03,100
Your poison

200
00:10:03,940 --> 00:10:05,540
can still be cured.

201
00:10:06,540 --> 00:10:09,260
I'll have Xiao deliver the prescription.

202
00:10:09,820 --> 00:10:12,020
You just need to take it on time.

203
00:10:13,100 --> 00:10:15,380
I still have to handle
the epidemic in Ning Capital.

204
00:10:15,660 --> 00:10:16,780
I'll take my leave.

205
00:10:18,180 --> 00:10:19,260
Xihe...

206
00:10:19,700 --> 00:10:20,780
Xihe...

207
00:10:22,980 --> 00:10:24,140
Xihe...

208
00:10:34,637 --> 00:10:36,539
(Twenty years ago)

209
00:10:36,540 --> 00:10:38,299
Your Majesty, you've just given birth.

210
00:10:38,300 --> 00:10:39,979
Please take care of your health.

211
00:10:39,980 --> 00:10:42,179
Burning the princess
is the Emperor's order.

212
00:10:42,180 --> 00:10:44,540
I'm just following orders.

213
00:10:46,420 --> 00:10:47,059
Quick!

214
00:10:47,060 --> 00:10:49,300
Stop her!

215
00:10:57,820 --> 00:10:59,220
Move!

216
00:11:15,540 --> 00:11:17,579
Your Majesty, this is an evil infant!

217
00:11:17,580 --> 00:11:20,420
If we don't burn her,
Ning State will fall!

218
00:11:25,340 --> 00:11:26,220
Your Majesty!

219
00:11:26,700 --> 00:11:29,059
Do not come any closer!

220
00:11:29,060 --> 00:11:32,459
Or I'll throw
the princess off the tower!

221
00:11:32,460 --> 00:11:35,100
You think I'd be
threatened by a eunuch like you?

222
00:11:40,340 --> 00:11:41,380
My child!

223
00:11:42,460 --> 00:11:43,500
My child!

224
00:11:58,180 --> 00:11:59,380
Don't be afraid.

225
00:12:00,300 --> 00:12:01,539
I am here.

226
00:12:01,540 --> 00:12:02,500
Quick!

227
00:12:02,700 --> 00:12:03,579
Surround her!

228
00:12:03,580 --> 00:12:05,260
Don't let that evil infant escape!

229
00:12:07,180 --> 00:12:08,620
Do not come any closer!

230
00:12:09,060 --> 00:12:10,140
Empress!

231
00:12:21,780 --> 00:12:22,900
Empress!

232
00:12:23,420 --> 00:12:24,620
It's windy outside.

233
00:12:25,060 --> 00:12:26,380
Come back to the palace with me.

234
00:12:27,060 --> 00:12:28,220
Your Majesty,

235
00:12:30,700 --> 00:12:32,699
this is our only child.

236
00:12:32,700 --> 00:12:34,500
Are you truly going to burn her?

237
00:12:36,700 --> 00:12:37,860
Your Majesty,

238
00:12:37,980 --> 00:12:39,179
the princess is stillborn.

239
00:12:39,180 --> 00:12:40,380
Nonsense!

240
00:12:40,580 --> 00:12:42,420
Can't you hear her crying?

241
00:12:42,900 --> 00:12:45,500
Empress, look carefully.

242
00:13:00,540 --> 00:13:01,660
My child...

243
00:13:02,660 --> 00:13:03,980
My child...

244
00:13:18,340 --> 00:13:19,500
Your Majesty,

245
00:13:20,300 --> 00:13:21,900
she's not dead!

246
00:13:26,300 --> 00:13:27,420
Your Majesty!

247
00:13:27,700 --> 00:13:29,140
I stake my life on this!

248
00:13:29,340 --> 00:13:31,579
This infant was born without a heart,

249
00:13:31,580 --> 00:13:32,819
covered in blade marks.

250
00:13:32,820 --> 00:13:35,260
Her eyes just flashed red.

251
00:13:35,300 --> 00:13:36,780
It's an ominous sign!

252
00:13:36,820 --> 00:13:38,099
If this evil infant is kept,

253
00:13:38,100 --> 00:13:39,660
it will bring disaster to the nation!

254
00:13:39,780 --> 00:13:42,099
Your Majesty, think of the greater good!

255
00:13:42,100 --> 00:13:43,500
Burn the infant at once

256
00:13:43,980 --> 00:13:46,740
to ensure the kingdom's peace!

257
00:13:46,820 --> 00:13:48,419
Burn the infant!

258
00:13:48,420 --> 00:13:50,500
Protect the kingdom!

259
00:13:56,220 --> 00:13:57,380
I will

260
00:13:58,300 --> 00:13:59,740
keep the child.

261
00:14:00,820 --> 00:14:01,900
Issue the decree.

262
00:14:02,300 --> 00:14:04,260
Name her Xihe.

263
00:14:04,420 --> 00:14:07,260
Record her in the royal lineage.

264
00:14:08,180 --> 00:14:08,939
Your Majesty!

265
00:14:08,940 --> 00:14:10,020
I said

266
00:14:11,420 --> 00:14:14,500
the child stays.

267
00:14:38,700 --> 00:14:39,860
(Ning,)

268
00:14:40,820 --> 00:14:43,260
(our daughter has grown up.)

269
00:14:49,100 --> 00:14:49,820
Zhao.

270
00:14:54,780 --> 00:14:56,260
Baobao, Xiao,

271
00:14:56,300 --> 00:14:57,659
stand guard outside.

272
00:14:57,660 --> 00:14:59,140
No one is to come in.

273
00:15:04,420 --> 00:15:07,500
This worm will burrow
into every blood vessel in your body,

274
00:15:08,060 --> 00:15:09,980
search through your organs

275
00:15:10,820 --> 00:15:12,620
until it finds the demon root.

276
00:15:14,060 --> 00:15:15,220
When that happens,

277
00:15:15,900 --> 00:15:17,579
the pain will consume you.

278
00:15:17,580 --> 00:15:19,780
It will feel like
your organs are being torn apart.

279
00:15:21,580 --> 00:15:22,819
Have you thought this through?

280
00:15:22,820 --> 00:15:24,500
If it saves the people and you,

281
00:15:25,420 --> 00:15:27,100
then pain is nothing.

282
00:15:55,220 --> 00:15:56,220
Xi...

283
00:15:56,780 --> 00:15:57,740
Xi...

284
00:15:59,180 --> 00:16:00,140
Xi...

285
00:16:05,460 --> 00:16:06,500
Xi...

286
00:16:09,940 --> 00:16:11,100
Are you okay?

287
00:16:11,820 --> 00:16:13,140
Don't worry about me.

288
00:16:13,220 --> 00:16:15,020
Find where the demon root is!

289
00:16:15,660 --> 00:16:16,620
Quick!

290
00:16:24,820 --> 00:16:25,900
How is it?

291
00:16:26,340 --> 00:16:28,260
Did you find it? Did you find it?

292
00:16:35,100 --> 00:16:37,860
The demon root isn't in your body.

293
00:16:41,287 --> 00:16:42,996
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

294
00:16:42,997 --> 00:16:45,846
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

295
00:16:45,847 --> 00:16:48,586
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

296
00:16:48,587 --> 00:16:50,216
♪Let the long shadows♪

297
00:16:50,217 --> 00:16:55,817
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

298
00:16:55,867 --> 00:16:57,466
♪If in a dream♪

299
00:16:57,467 --> 00:17:00,226
♪I can hear your voice♪

300
00:17:00,227 --> 00:17:03,076
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

301
00:17:03,077 --> 00:17:05,676
♪Let it be us♪

302
00:17:05,677 --> 00:17:10,466
♪drawing endlessly close♪

303
00:17:10,467 --> 00:17:12,226
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

304
00:17:12,227 --> 00:17:14,877
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

305
00:17:15,097 --> 00:17:17,816
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

306
00:17:17,817 --> 00:17:19,466
♪Not even in time♪

307
00:17:19,467 --> 00:17:25,126
♪to tell you how I feel♪

308
00:17:25,127 --> 00:17:26,666
♪If the rain won't stop♪

309
00:17:26,667 --> 00:17:29,416
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

310
00:17:29,417 --> 00:17:32,386
♪Let love go on♪

311
00:17:32,387 --> 00:17:34,936
♪Until forever♪

312
00:17:34,937 --> 00:17:39,576
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

313
00:17:39,577 --> 00:17:42,186
♪Until forever♪

314
00:17:42,187 --> 00:17:49,297
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
